{
  "element": "parseResult",
  "content": [
    {
      "element": "category",
      "meta": {
        "classes": [
          "api"
        ],
        "title": "Parameters API"
      },
      "attributes": {
        "meta": [
          {
            "element": "member",
            "meta": {
              "classes": [
                "user"
              ]
            },
            "content": {
              "key": {
                "element": "string",
                "content": "FORMAT"
              },
              "value": {
                "element": "string",
                "content": "1A"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "element": "copy",
          "content": "In this installment of the API Blueprint course we will discuss how to describe URI parameters.\n\nBut first let's add more messages to our system. For that we would need\nintroduce an message identifier â€“ id. This id will be our parameter when\ncommunicating with our API about messages.\n\n## API Blueprint\n\n+ [Previous: Requests](06.%20Requests.md)\n\n+ [This: Raw API Blueprint](https://raw.github.com/apiaryio/api-blueprint/master/examples/07.%20Parameters.md)\n\n+ [Next: Attributes](08.%20Attributes.md)\n\n"
        },
        {
          "element": "category",
          "meta": {
            "classes": [
              "resourceGroup"
            ],
            "title": "Messages"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "element": "copy",
              "content": "Group of all messages-related resources.\n\n"
            },
            {
              "element": "resource",
              "meta": {
                "title": "My Message"
              },
              "attributes": {
                "href": "/message/{id}",
                "hrefVariables": {
                  "element": "hrefVariables",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "element": "member",
                      "meta": {
                        "description": "An unique identifier of the message."
                      },
                      "content": {
                        "key": {
                          "element": "string",
                          "content": "id"
                        },
                        "value": {
                          "element": "number",
                          "content": 1
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "element": "copy",
                  "content": "Here we have added the message `id` parameter as an \n[URI Template variable](http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6570) in the Message\nresource's URI. Note the parameter name `id` is enclosed in curly brackets. We\nwill discuss this parameter in the `Parameters` section below, where we will\nalso set its example value to `1` and declare it of an arbitrary 'number' type.\n\n"
                },
                {
                  "element": "transition",
                  "meta": {
                    "title": "Retrieve a Message"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "element": "httpTransaction",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "httpRequest",
                          "meta": {
                            "title": "Plain Text Message"
                          },
                          "attributes": {
                            "method": "GET",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Accept"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "text/plain"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": []
                        },
                        {
                          "element": "httpResponse",
                          "attributes": {
                            "statusCode": "200",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Content-Type"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "text/plain"
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "X-My-Message-Header"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "42"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "element": "asset",
                              "meta": {
                                "classes": [
                                  "messageBody"
                                ]
                              },
                              "attributes": {
                                "contentType": "text/plain"
                              },
                              "content": "Hello World!\n"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "element": "httpTransaction",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "httpRequest",
                          "meta": {
                            "title": "JSON Message"
                          },
                          "attributes": {
                            "method": "GET",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Accept"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "application/json"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": []
                        },
                        {
                          "element": "httpResponse",
                          "attributes": {
                            "statusCode": "200",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Content-Type"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "application/json"
                                    }
                                  }
                                },
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "X-My-Message-Header"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "42"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "element": "asset",
                              "meta": {
                                "classes": [
                                  "messageBody"
                                ]
                              },
                              "attributes": {
                                "contentType": "application/json"
                              },
                              "content": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"message\": \"Hello World!\"\n}\n"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "element": "transition",
                  "meta": {
                    "title": "Update a Message"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "element": "httpTransaction",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "httpRequest",
                          "meta": {
                            "title": "Update Plain Text Message"
                          },
                          "attributes": {
                            "method": "PUT",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Content-Type"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "text/plain"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "element": "asset",
                              "meta": {
                                "classes": [
                                  "messageBody"
                                ]
                              },
                              "attributes": {
                                "contentType": "text/plain"
                              },
                              "content": "All your base are belong to us.\n"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "element": "httpResponse",
                          "attributes": {
                            "statusCode": "204"
                          },
                          "content": []
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "element": "httpTransaction",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "httpRequest",
                          "meta": {
                            "title": "Update JSON Message"
                          },
                          "attributes": {
                            "method": "PUT",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Content-Type"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "application/json"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "element": "asset",
                              "meta": {
                                "classes": [
                                  "messageBody"
                                ]
                              },
                              "attributes": {
                                "contentType": "application/json"
                              },
                              "content": "{ \"message\": \"All your base are belong to us.\" }\n"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "element": "httpResponse",
                          "attributes": {
                            "statusCode": "204"
                          },
                          "content": []
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "element": "resource",
              "meta": {
                "title": "All My Messages"
              },
              "attributes": {
                "href": "/messages{?limit}"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "element": "copy",
                  "content": "A resource representing all of my messages in the system.\n\nWe have added the query URI template parameter - `limit`. This parameter is\nused for limiting the number of results returned by some actions on this\nresource. It does not affect every possible action of this resource, therefore\nwe will discuss it only at the particular action level below.\n\n"
                },
                {
                  "element": "transition",
                  "meta": {
                    "title": "Retrieve all Messages"
                  },
                  "attributes": {
                    "hrefVariables": {
                      "element": "hrefVariables",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "member",
                          "meta": {
                            "description": "The maximum number of results to return."
                          },
                          "attributes": {
                            "typeAttributes": [
                              "optional"
                            ]
                          },
                          "content": {
                            "key": {
                              "element": "string",
                              "content": "limit"
                            },
                            "value": {
                              "element": "number",
                              "attributes": {
                                "default": "20"
                              }
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "element": "httpTransaction",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "element": "httpRequest",
                          "attributes": {
                            "method": "GET"
                          },
                          "content": []
                        },
                        {
                          "element": "httpResponse",
                          "attributes": {
                            "statusCode": "200",
                            "headers": {
                              "element": "httpHeaders",
                              "content": [
                                {
                                  "element": "member",
                                  "content": {
                                    "key": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "Content-Type"
                                    },
                                    "value": {
                                      "element": "string",
                                      "content": "application/json"
                                    }
                                  }
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          },
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "element": "asset",
                              "meta": {
                                "classes": [
                                  "messageBody"
                                ]
                              },
                              "attributes": {
                                "contentType": "application/json"
                              },
                              "content": "[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"message\": \"Hello World!\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"message\": \"Time is an illusion. Lunchtime doubly so.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": 3,\n    \"message\": \"So long, and thanks for all the fish.\"\n  }\n]\n"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
